.TH "mdiobus_modify" 9 "mdiobus_modify" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mdiobus_modify \- Convenience function for modifying a given mdio device register
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mdiobus_modify
.BI "(struct mii_bus *bus "  ","
.BI "int addr "  ","
.BI "u32 regnum "  ","
.BI "u16 mask "  ","
.BI "u16 set "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bus" 12
the mii_bus struct
.IP "addr" 12
the phy address
.IP "regnum" 12
register number to write
.IP "mask" 12
bit mask of bits to clear
.IP "set" 12
bit mask of bits to set
